Super-hero-confessions is a blog where you can submit your confessions/personal opinions about any of the super hero movies, comics, television shows, cartoons, etc.

The confessions that are posted are those that are submitted; not the opinions of the blog owners. All the confessions will be anonymous when posted. Feel free to submit photos along with your confession if you would like as well.

If you want us to see a post tag it with either #superheroconfessions or #superhero confessions

title: Something I want to see
body:
This could be the very end of Captain Marvel, a jump to 20 or 30 or however many years it is later after the actual events of the main plot. Carol Danvers gets Nick Fury’s …  intergalactic page or whatever and comes to Earth. Quick montage of getting oriented to the total chaos that’s going down and finding out where to go now–in a matter of minutes.

Cut to Wakanda, where everyone is still reeling from having ALMOST WON and then lost everything. Steve is still sitting on the ground, trying to process what happened to Bucky, trying to process “we lost.” And then BAM Carol appears in a blaze of kickassery, radiating grim determination. There may be a quick moment of introduction, as everyone remaining goes “who the hell are you?” and she says something along the lines of “I’m Captain Marvel, Fury called me in because you guys weren’t enough, let’s talk plans.”

Then she walks over to Steve, and there’s a quick exchange of “Captain.” “Captain,” and then Captain Carol “fall down seven times, get up eight” Danvers pulls Captain “I can do this all day” Steve Rogers to his feet, and we cut to credits.

And then we all scream for a year until Avengers 4 comes out.

title: Sickness
body:
Yay! Super fun to work on and overall an interesting prompt, go and check it out, my first work for the Marvel Cinematic Universe.

Prompt from @ironbar36: “Genie AU of Captain Marvel going to meet Doctor Strange because she’s having an issue with her wish granting abilities. Just make up something quirky I guess it’s stress related or like she can’t sleep well and it’s affecting her powers.”

https://archiveofourown.org/works/16548044

Please Read&Review!
